text: Scum with Boundaries is the second studio album by American rock duo The I.L.Y's. The album was released on July 16, 2016, through YouTube and SoundCloud. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== ;The I.L.Y's * Zach Hill – vocals, drums, keyboards, guitar, production * Andy Morin – guitar, bass, engineering ==References== ==External links== * Category:The I.L.Y's albums Category:2016 albums Category:Self-released albums
